		PINHEIRO, JoÃo Pedro Sant´anna<sup>1</sup>; FERNANDES, Marcos Tadeu Parron<sup>2</sup>; LARANGEIRA, Lino Luis Sanches<sup>3</sup>; FERNANDES, Karen Barros Parron<sup>4</sup>		<BR>
